<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.1.2">
<l>miṉṉu māḻiyaṅ kaiyavaṉ ceyyava ḷuṟaitaru tirumārpaṉ</l>
<l>paṉṉu nāṉmaṟaip palaporu ḷākiya paraṉiṭam varaiccāral</l>
<l>piṉṉu mātavip pantalil peṭaivarap piṇiyaviḻ kamalattu</l>
<l>teṉṉa veṉṟuvaṇ ṭiṉṉicai muraltaru tiruvayin tirapuramē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of the supreme who became the many meanings</l>
<l rend="indent">of the recited four Vedas,</l>
<l>The one in whose fine hand is the shining discus, the one whose sacred chest</l>
<l rend="indent">is where the Red Lady naturally dwells,</l>
<l>Is Tiruvayintirapuram which yields the sweet music of a bee</l>
<l rend="indent">on a lotus with a loosened [bud] knot saying ‘humm’</l>
<l>To coax [his] mate from the canopy of mādhavi [creepers]</l>
<l rend="indent">which crisscross the mountain slopes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
